      "title": "Sri Lanka shares gain over 1-pct in mid-day trade",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka\u2019s shares rose over 1 percent within the first hour of trade on Tuesday (July 19), Colombo Stock Exchange data showed.",
        "The main All Share Price Index gained 1.36% or 102.68 points to 7,639.29 at 1138 hours.",
        "The most liquid S&P SL20 gained 1.60% or 38.86 points to 2,461.94.",
        "Top gainers were Commercial Banka, Sampath Bank and Richard Pieris. (Colombo/Jul19/2022)"
      ],
